    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After yet another night of brooding over his wife's murder, Edgar McGee receives a mysterious letter under the door of his private investigator's office. Rising music star Minnie Williams has asked you to investigate her “own murder”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plunge into the gloomy San Antonio of the 70s, search multiple locations, solve puzzles and interview the victim's relatives to uncover the killer's identity! Will you be able to unravel the truth from the lies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/cae53b646836408c581af77b46f7c5fb.avif?t=1759747106\" width=463 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/2b59126898413aaec180ee5bce18dd1a.poster.avif?t=1759747106\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/2b59126898413aaec180ee5bce18dd1a.webm?t=1759747106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/2b59126898413aaec180ee5bce18dd1a.mp4?t=1759747106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the role of a disillusioned private detective. Since your wife's murder almost 3 years ago, you've been a shadow of your former self. Spending your nights re-examining the report on the investigation into her murder, you're on the verge of going out of business. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So when Minnie Williams asks you to investigate her own murder, you can't afford to miss the opportunity to remake yourself and solve the case.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/24640d7ef9a0dc4c5f57af7f5b00adaa.avif?t=1759747106\" width=463 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/ba33a5c0f1f8af90d70e75d22265c25c.poster.avif?t=1759747106\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/ba33a5c0f1f8af90d70e75d22265c25c.webm?t=1759747106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/ba33a5c0f1f8af90d70e75d22265c25c.mp4?t=1759747106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interview a dozen suspects with unique backgrounds and characters, choosing from a variety of multi-layered dialogues. Explore their homes or workplaces for clues and evidence. Make decisions, solve puzzles and find out what happened to Minnie Williams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/49bcf5b8f23249310a7bcee0be8fa3d7.avif?t=1759747106\" width=463 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/7f178de13745707439aae205caa929df.poster.avif?t=1759747106\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/7f178de13745707439aae205caa929df.webm?t=1759747106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130420/extras/7f178de13745707439aae205caa929df.mp4?t=1759747106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel back in time to 1971 with this dark investigative game that transports you to the hippie years!  Explore unique locations and interact with dozens of objects straight out of a bygone era, including a working cassette player and a working turntable! </p>",
